Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:58.76,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Foggy London...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:24:03.41,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,a young man visited Holmes\Nwhile he was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:07.64,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked Holmes to look for\Nthree missing students.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:10.61,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,When Holmes began the investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.75,0:24:13.65,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,he found traces\Nof them unexpectedly.
